stions, lachez vous sur l\u2019adresse&nbsp;<strong>contact@passetonbillet.fr<\/strong> <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>A tr\u00e8s vite,<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>L&rsquo;\u00e9quipe PasseTonBillet<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Cyril, Axel et Julien<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u00ab&nbsp;Les Billets des uns font le bonheur des autres&nbsp;\u00bb<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Retrouvez-nous Facebook:<\/strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"http:\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20150315223341\/http:\/\/www.facebook.com\/passetonbillet\"><strong>http:\/\/www.facebook.com\/passetonbillet<\/strong><\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>6 mois apr\u00e8s le lancement de la nouvelle version du site PasseTonBillet, nous sommes heureux de vous annoncer le retour du blog, un espace d&rsquo;expression pour mieux vous informer sur le site et le march\u00e9 de la revente de billets d&rsquo;occasion.. En seulement 6 mois, nous sommes tr\u00e8s satisfait car [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[3],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/blog.passetonbillet.fr\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/74"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/blog.passetonbillet.fr\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/blog.passetonbillet.fr\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/blog.passetonbillet.fr\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/blog.passetonbillet.fr\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=74"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/blog.passetonbillet.fr\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/74\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":77,"href":"https:\/\/blog.passetonbillet.fr\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/74\/revisions\/77"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/blog.passetonbillet.fr\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=74"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/blog.passetonbillet.fr\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\